<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">3. Cookies & Analytics</h2>
<p>
Our website may use cookies and analytics tools to understand user behavior and improve functionality. These tools collect non-sensitive technical information and do not access personal files on your device.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">4. Data Sharing</h2>
<p>
We do not sell or rent your personal information. Your data may only be shared with service providers strictly for operational purposes (e.g., communication platforms).
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3">5. Data Security</h2>
<p>
We implement reasonable technical and administrative safeguards to protect your data. However, no digital transmission method guarantees absolute security.
</p>

